      <h3>CSS-in-JS</h3>
      <p>
        We chose a CSS-in-JS solution because it provides scoped and modular
        styles, preventing global namespace pollution and ensuring that styles
        are tightly coupled with their respective components. This approach also
        allows for dynamic styling based on component state or props.
      </p>

    switch themes and adjust styles dynamically.
